* Short history of Go

Initially it was developed internally at Google from ~2007

Authors Ken Thompson, Rob Pike and Robert Griesemer

Open source since 2009

Stable release 1.0 since 2012

* Go compatibility promise

Guarantees backwards compatibility: any program that runs on Go 1.0 can be compiled and runs in Go 1.x

